snippet.title: MXGP PRO Announcement Trailer
snippet.description:
DISCOVER MORE: http://mxgpvideogame.com/
June 29, 2018 on PlayStation 4, Xbox One, PC
MXGP PRO is a brand-new start, designed to meet the need of the most demanding fans to relive the real spirit of Motocross. Based on the community feedback, players will be able to setup each single parameter of their bike basing on real values and metrics. This
is what PRO is set to be, a videogame with a completely new soul!
